{"tid":1603316,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"做人要有目標！","createTime":"2019-09-29T15:58:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T16:00:17.000Z","uid":319380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5399d96979aee98490f0483b3f50d0cd042ba0e3","tid":1603316,"uid":319380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:58:44.000Z","msg":"我覺得我地每次行動，要有一個好明確嘅目標。<br />\n<br />\n例如612，阻立法會二讀；71，攻立法會。<br />\n<br />\n睇左咁多日嘅post，我一直以為今日遊行嘅目標係「全球反極權」<br />\n全球有超過24個國家響應<br />\n作為主辦單位，無理由我地無人出黎<br />\n所以就算知道黑警早已係港島設防，我地都堅持出港島<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我完全無想過今日會有咁多人出黎<br />\n尤其係無申請不反對通知書嘅情況下<br />\n竟然有咁多中年人參加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n看到國旗海，再看到遊行人潮由灣仔去到銅鑼灣<br />\n其實我覺得今日嘅目標已達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知我咁嘅想法好和理非<br />\n但每次睇到前線嘅人受傷及被捕，個心真係好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望前線每次行動前好好定一個明確目標，完成就走人<br />\n留嘅時間越長，對你地越不利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n10月1日，希望大家諗一諗目標係乜<br />\n你地期望10月2日嘅報紙頭條寫乜<br />\n就係10月1日我地要做嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />賀佢老母=落中共面<br />\n落人面，除了衝鋒陷陣外，我相信還有好多野可以做<br />\n精神折磨，有時比肉體折磨傷害更大。(白色恐怖就係例子)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家可以集思廣益一下。<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 謝謝旗手及準備海報嘅義工，你地真係好勁！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VuMyZZS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVuMyZZS.jpg&h=94ec0840&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c41f74cf431175d89b330c47161a09f26f24b5b","tid":1603316,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:59:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0e532775a7bd247986e068956a9d3279db49002f","tid":1603316,"uid":314509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:00:17.000Z","msg":"10.1目標之一：對準鏡頭讀宣言<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zhwF7kd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzhwF7kd.jpg&h=5781479b&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v40Ly0d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv40Ly0d.jpg&h=3864b67f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">原po在此：<br />\n【重要行動/文宣】十一光復香港宣言<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1595334\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1595334</a></span>"}]}